Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:38.36,Ep_Title,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,600)}The Hero's Melancholy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.29,0:01:34.82,Default - Top,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I listened to the recording.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:36.45,Default - Top,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty conclusive evidence, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:38.76,Default - Top,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dobu only named my brother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:41.45,sign_2313_4_Little_Daimon,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Little Daimon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:40.73,Italics,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he lied out of desperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.73,0:01:45.01,Italics,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,All we know for sure is that Dobu is \Nplanning to rob a bank. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.01,0:01:47.27,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Your love for your brother is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:49.55,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,But that's good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.55,0:01:51.59,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I want to let Dobu keep going for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:53.33,Italics,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you now, Odokawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.33,0:01:55.69,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,My friend may have been kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.69,0:01:57.09,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to rescue him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:58.61,Italics,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a case, Odokawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.61,0:02:00.01,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Evil is afoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.27,Italics,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's unbelievably evil. And if evil is \Nafoot, then it's time for me to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:04.57,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:08.06,Italics,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Punishing evil is my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:09.11,Italics,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:10.25,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Shibaura Wharf.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:11.19,Italics,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Outside my jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:12.00,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:12.84,Italics,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:16.50,Italics,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt you're aware, but there's this thing \Ncalled extra-jurisdictional authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:20.09,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome to help as Little \NDaimon the private citizen,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:22.79,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,but for now, I don't need \Nhelp from the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:24.58,Italics,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's incredibly insulting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.70,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing this to exterminate evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:28.96,Italics,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't tear it out by the \Nroots, it just comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:31.46,sign_3518_29_Little_Daimon,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Little Daimon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:31.46,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. You're quick on the uptake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:33.42,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to get rid of\Nthem all in one fell swoop,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:35.22,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,so I need the cops to wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:36.32,Italics,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:39.12,Italics,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's frustrating, but if the alternative \Nis being overrun by evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:40.75,Italics,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,then I'll have to turn a blind eye to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:42.77,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell did you learn those words?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:44.45,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a hurry. I'll talk to you later.
